This is a true breakthrough in coriander cultivation - a cultivar specifically bred to resist bolting and produce a continuous, abundant harvest of the large, citrusy, and potent leaves essential to Southeast Asian cuisine. ‘Metro-Pak Chee’ delivers the authentic, robust flavour of Thai coriander with the reliability and compact form demanded by the urban gardener.

